            . I am a servant to Mr. Allen; on the 22d of October the prisoner pawned a clock with me for six shillings. I am positive the prisoner is the woman. This is the clock.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181410260055"></xptr>Prosecutor. This is my watch, and this clock is my wife's.</p>
